  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for xorg-x11-server",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for xorg-x11-server fixes the following issues:\n\n- CreateSaverWindow Use-After-Free Information Disclosure. (bsc#1266301)\n- DRI2 DRIGetBuffers/DRIGetBuffersWithFormat Out-Of-Bounds Write. (bsc#1266302)\n- Font Alias Stack-based Buffer Overflow. (bsc#1266294)\n- GLX ChangeDrawableAttributes Out-Of-Bounds Read/Write. (bsc#1266300)\n- XKB Key Types Stack-based Buffer Overflow. (bsc#1266296)\n- XKB SetMap Request Stack-based Buffer Overflow. (bsc#1266297)\n- XSYNC Use-After-Free in FreeCounter(). (bsc#1266298)\n- XSYNC Use-After-Free in miSyncDestroyFence(). (bsc#1266295)\n- XSYNC Use-After-Free in SyncChangeCounter(). (bsc#1266299)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
